<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Musicmining file upload</title>
    <style>
    body{
        font-family:'Courier New';
        font-size: 12pt;
        color:white;
        background-image:url("image/mm_bg_ios.png");
        background-position:center center;
        opacity:0.9;
        background-size: 100%;
        text-align: center;
        vertical-align: center;
        line-height:150%;
      }
      </style>
</head>

<body>
<center><br><br><br>
  <img src="image/final_logo.jpg" width=60 height=60>
    <form enctype="multipart/form-data"  action="/uploads"  method="post">
<br><br>
      *가수 :
      <input type="text" id="musician_name" style="background-color:transparent;" name="musician_name" ><br>
      그룹 :
      <input type="text" id="group_name" style="background-color:transparent;" name="group_name" ><br>
      피처링 :
      <input type="text" id="featuring_name" style="background-color:transparent;" name="featuring_name" ><br>

      *음악 제목 :
      <input type="text" id="title"  style="background-color:transparent;" name="title" ><br>
      가사 :
      <input type="text" id="lyrics"  style="background-color:transparent;" name="lyrics" ><br>
      *하이라이트 비디오 :
      <input type="file" style="background-color:transparent;" name="highlight_video" /><br>
      *썸네일 이미지 :
      <input type="file" style="background-color:transparent;" name="thumbnail" /><br>
      *음원 파일 :
      <input type="file" style="background-color:transparent;" name="music" /><br>

      장르 :
      <input type="text" id="genre"  style="background-color:transparent;" name="genre" ><br>

      작사 :
      <input type="text" id="lyricist" style="background-color:transparent;" name="lyricist" ><br>
      작곡 :
      <input type="text" id="composer" style="background-color:transparent;" name="composer" ><br>

      *앨범 제목 :
      <input type="text" id="album_name" style="background-color:transparent;" name="album_name" ><br>
      앨범 정보 :
      <input type="text" id="album_info" style="background-color:transparent;" name="album_info" ><br>
      발매 일자 :
      <input type="text" id="sale_date" style="background-color:transparent;" name="sale_date" ><br>
      *앨범 커버 이미지 :
      <input type="file"  style="background-color:transparent;"  name="album_image" /><br>

      <br>
      <input type="submit" value="Upload" name="submit"> <br>
      <br><b>*은 필수사항입니다.</b>
    </form>
</center>
</body>


</html>
